label: Hoser, Raymond.  2016. A long overdue taxonomic rearrangement of the Uromastycinae (Squamata: Sauria: Agamidae), … correcting a repeated inadvertent typographical error and ensuring the nomenclatural availability of the new name Euanedwardssaurus as well as the correct names or spellings for a tribe of Blindsnakes, a Python and a Kukri snake. Australasian Journal of Herpetology 33: 20-22.
